">2. </div><div class="t m1208 x55 h4 y12b6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did Paul rebuke the wicked spirit? What was </div><div class="t mc2 x5d h4 yd2a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the result? Verse 18. Note 2. </div><div class="t m2b6 x60 h4 yb8a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m2c35 x55 h4 ye02 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did the owners of the slave girl do to Paul </div><div class="t m1349 x5d h4 y9c6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Silas? What charge did they make against them? </div><div class="t m1670 x5d h4 y758 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verses 19-21. </div><div class="t ma2 x60 h4 y992 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1c6a x55 h4 y1020 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who joined with them in the attack against Paul </div><div class="t m1b7e x5d h4 yf56 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Silas? What did the magistrates do? Verse 22. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
